item.title: CVE-2023-5834|2024-08-02T08:14:24.694Z -- hashicorp -- vagrant
item.description: HashiCorp Vagrant's Windows installer targeted a custom location with a non-protected path that could be junctioned, introducing potential for unauthorized file system writes. Fixed in Vagrant 2.4.0.
